Get to know the rules of football
Do you want to become a (better) referee? Are you a football player, fan, coach or journalist? Do you want to review a situation while watching a match on TV or live in the stadium? Then you need to know the Laws of the Game!

The Laws of the Game - accessible to everyone
Our app allows you to:
- read the full Laws of the Game on your mobile device (online and offline);
- compare the latest rules with the previous edition and see what has changed;
- read all the recent Law changes including detailed explanations;
- test your knowledge in the Q&A section;
- add your own notes and mark favourite chapters;
- easily switch between languages and/or Laws editions.
